      "writtenOn": "2020-07-16T11:26:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not a huge fan of this approach.  It feels a little sneaky to be directly accessing the database, and I think it could make things brittle if we wanted to change implementations.  Could we use the HTTP frontend instead?",
